results.name: Table, T(n,k) is the number of connected categories with n morphisms and k objects.
comment: Connected in the sense that if the morphism direction and composition is ignored, resulting in a multigraph, that multigraph is connected.
xref: Cf. A125696, A125698 (row sums), A110654 (row lengths), A058129 (column 1), A125700 (diagonal sums), A125702 (T(2n-1, n)).
results.author: _Franklin T. Adams-Watters_ and _Christian G. Bower_, Jan 05 2007
